Here,the men's only choice is between German bullets and ours.

162
00:25:54,330 --> 00:25:55,890
But there's another way.

163
00:25:56,040 --> 00:26:00,040
The way of courage.The way of love of the motherland.

164
00:26:00,040 --> 00:26:01,770
We must publish the army newspaper again.

165
00:26:01,910 --> 00:26:06,280
We must tell magnificent stories. Stories that extol... sacrifice,bravery.

166
00:26:06,280 --> 00:26:08,610
We must make them believe in the victory.

167
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:13,380
We must give them hope, pride,a desire to fight.

168
00:26:13,690 --> 00:26:17,120
Yes,we need to make examples.

169
00:26:17,260 --> 00:26:19,590
But examples to follow.

170
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:21,550
What we need...

171
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:24,820
are heroes.

172
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:31,100
Do you know any heroes around here?

173
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:35,470
Yes,comrade, I know one.

174
00:26:41,110 --> 00:26:42,580
That's me!

175
00:26:42,980 --> 00:26:46,420
"Vassili Zaitsev." That's me!

176
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,420
No,you're not dreaming.

177
