It's your name.

178
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:52,690
We made the front page.

179
00:26:53,330 --> 00:26:55,380
They haven't changed a word.

180
00:26:56,300 --> 00:26:59,390
Do you have any idea what this means?

181
00:26:59,770 --> 00:27:02,100
It's not the back page, it's not the second page,

182
00:27:02,230 --> 00:27:03,200
It's the front page.

183
