Yes,careful of my-  careful of my glasses,please. They're new. Sorry,sir.

202
00:27:53,720 --> 00:27:56,950
- I'm famous! We're famous! - I'm famous! I'm famous!

203
00:27:57,090 --> 00:27:59,060
Vassili, the young shepherd from the Urals,

204
00:27:59,190 --> 00:28:00,250
killed his 12th German officer today.

205
