1000
01:55:15,930 --> 01:55:19,390
Where is he?

1001
01:55:19,890 --> 01:55:21,420
Where's the major?

1002
01:55:21,560 --> 01:55:23,810
A few inches from your face.

1003
01:55:23,810 --> 01:55:29,440
I've been such a fool, Vassili.

1004
01:55:29,660 --> 01:55:33,770
Man will always be man.

1005
01:55:33,770 --> 01:55:35,940
There is no new man.

1006
01:55:37,280 --> 01:55:40,510
We tried so hard to create a society that was equal,

1007
01:55:40,650 --> 01:55:43,630
where there'd be nothing to envy your neighbor.

1008
01:55:43,630 --> 01:55:48,090
But there's always something to envy.

1009
01:55:48,660 --> 01:55:50,620
A smile...

1010
01:55:51,130 --> 01:55:52,920
a friendship.

1011
01:55:54,090 --> 01:55:57,960
Something you don't have and want to appropriate.

1012
01:55:58,300 --> 01:56:02,700
In this world even a Soviet one

1013
01:56:02,840 --> 01:56:05,400
there will always be rich and poor.

1014
01:56:06,970 --> 01:56:09,240
Rich in gifts...

1015
01:56:10,440 --> 01:56:12,540
poor in gifts.

1016
01:56:13,450 --> 01:56:15,350
Rich in love...

1017
01:56:16,880 --> 01:56:18,880
poor in love.

1018
01:56:24,860 --> 01:56:27,450
Tania isn't coming back.

1019
01:56:28,960 --> 01:56:31,690
She's dead,Vassili.

1020
01:56:39,810 --> 01:56:42,210
She was cut down by shrapnel.

1021
01:56:42,340 --> 01:56:47,250
It was quick.I don't think she even saw it coming.

1022
01:56:47,780 --> 01:56:49,720
She was on her way back to you.

1023
01:56:49,850 --> 01:56:53,250
As soon as she had seen Mrs.Filipov to the boats,

1024
01:56:53,390 --> 01:56:55,580
she was coming back for you.

1025
01:56:55,790 --> 01:57:00,590
She was right. You're a good man,Vassili.

1026
01:57:04,030 --> 01:57:06,660
I want to help you, Vassili.

1027
01:57:06,800 --> 01:57:09,200
Let me do one last thing.

1028
01:57:09,340 --> 01:57:12,740
Something useful for a change.

1029
01:57:17,780 --> 01:57:19,340
Let me show you where the major is.

1030
01:57:19,510 --> 01:57:20,950
Don't do that.

1031
01:57:21,150 --> 01:57:22,380
Don't do that!

1032
02:01:36,600 --> 02:01:40,100
Today,February3,1943, is an ominous day for Hitler...

1033
02:01:40,240 --> 02:01:46,250
and the endless columns of hundreds of thousands of German prisoners.

1034
02:01:46,250 --> 02:01:54,350
It is an unforgettable day of hope for our motherland.

1035
02:02:02,660 --> 02:02:06,890
After 180 days of heroic combat...

1036
02:02:07,030 --> 02:02:09,370
in the market city of Stalingrad,

1037
02:02:09,540 --> 02:02:14,470
and as a result of the valor and self-sacrifice of our soldiers,

1038
02:02:14,640 --> 02:02:17,770
the commander of our glorious Red Army...

1039
02:02:17,910 --> 02:02:26,940
received the unconditional surrender... of the German fascist invaders.

1040
02:02:37,430 --> 02:02:38,660
Sorry. No,young man,

1041
02:02:39,430 --> 02:02:43,460
- I cannot find...a matching name in the book. - Could you check again?

1042
02:02:43,600 --> 02:02:46,000
- This is the address and her name. - She is not here.

1043
02:02:46,140 --> 02:02:50,800
Yes,this is our address, but we don't have her anymore.

1044
02:02:51,010 --> 02:02:52,740
- This is the address. She's been here. - I'm so sorry.

1045
02:02:52,880 --> 02:02:54,400
She wrote to me.

1046
02:02:54,550 --> 02:02:56,540
I looked three times. She's not here.

1047
02:02:56,680 --> 02:03:01,120
Believe me,there is no Tania Chernova. I can't help you.

1048
02:03:01,250 --> 02:03:04,380
I'm so sorry.

